File: pycaptive
Service: Nginx

- Instruction: depending on the distro, it must resides in /etc/nginx/sites-available and obviously, having a symlink in /etc/nginx/sites-enabled.
- After the setup, run: nginx -t && nginx -s reload

File: pycaptive.conf
Service: Supervisor

- Instruction: depending on the distro, it must resides in /etc/supervisor/conf.d/.
- After the setup, run: supervisorctl reread && supervisorctl update && supervisorctl status
